---
title: Fillet Steak & Creamy Bacon-Mushroom Sauce with Golden Wedges & Nutty Greens
description: Dish up tender premium beef eye fillet with a divine creamy mushroom and bacon sauce, plus crispy wedges and sautéed greens complement the rich flavors. It's hard to beat simple and classic, but it's sure easy to give it a snazzy makeover.
